# Professional Biography

I am a versatile software developer with experience across multiple companies and programming environments. Specializing in backend and scripting development, Aidan brings expertise in C++, Python, and C# to solve complex engineering challenges. His work spans 3D modeling, point cloud processing, and particle data integration, reflecting a strong foundation in both software and hardware systems.

As a club leader with a passion for robotics and computer architecture, Aidan combines technical acumen with trained soft skills to manage projects, coordinate timelines, and ensure clear communication across teams. His energetic approach to learning and problem-solving fuels his ability to adapt quickly and deliver results with precision and creativity.

